node.text: Napoleon Curry voted and so did I. Only a couple more days y’all! Let’s get to the polls. Let your voices be heard! Let’s do it! 😆😂#happyhalloween #whenweallvote

node.text:
I’m so excited to invite all of you to Sweet July’s first annual “Sweet Retreat” happening all month long starting this Sunday, July 4th!

This virtual retreat is the perfect excuse to indulge in a little self-care and recharge with the Sweet July community. With a focus on healthy eating, sleep, fitness and mindfulness - we’ve packed this month full of special guests, recipes and workouts to keep you feeling and looking your best. Join us, it’s all happening over at @sweetjuly! 🎉🎉🎉 #sweetretreat2021 #sweetretreat
